name: Welcome to Batavia
description:
Irina goes after her brother, James. They laughed and ran. Irina loves James, her only brother. They played on until they didn't realize that a war was going on. 

--

Monas was built in 1961 on the idea of ​​Soekarno (Indonesia's 1st president) who wanted a monument to commemorate the struggle of the Indonesian people against the invaders.
